Ant-Man and Damage Control find themselves face-to-face with the ever dangerous, ever deadly DRAGON MAN--who is neither a "dragon" nor a "man." You'd think Eric O'Grady, our resident "Irredeemable" Ant-Man would be able to relate to someone with such a dishonest name--but one look at our cover will tell you--that's NOT the case.
